</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF646ADBFA58900B16A5BDA9" pageId="159" pageNumber="920" type="breeding">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF646ADBFA58900B16A5BDA9" blockId="159.[1443,2651,1144,1969]" pageId="159" pageNumber="920">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF646ADBFA58900B182BBD41" bold="true" box="[1444,1579,1618,1651]" pageId="159" pageNumber="920">Breeding.</emphasis>
Gracile Tube-nosed Bats reportedly give birth to two young in May; lactating females have been collected from mid-May to mid-July.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
