<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF646ADBFA5A90A916E7BC0B" pageId="159" pageNumber="920" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF646ADBFA5A90A916E7BC0B" blockId="159.[1443,2651,1144,1969]" pageId="159" pageNumber="920">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF646ADBFA5A90A91903BC23" bold="true" box="[1446,1795,1776,1809]" pageId="159" pageNumber="920">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Gracile Tube-nosed Bat does not seem to face any major threats.
</paragraph>
